results.deck: Griptonite is a video game developer.
results.description: Griptonite is a game developer based in Kirkland, Washington. Most of their work has been with licensed games. And most of the time they deal with ports of games. Their most recent port was Shrek Forever After. Their most recent game that went to every console was Where the Wild Things Are.
